Recently, I've been just thinking about the value of food preferences. It is difficult to match tastes.

I'm worried... yeah, just worried―― I should stop doing that...
I'm worried about, well―― um, I'll better stop it.

I've always liked cooking, but lately I've been especially into cooking. He eats a lot, so it gives me a sense of pride.

Recently, I often accompany him with his camera. I think I should try taking pictures of myself, too, instead of just being photographed.
I'm not a picky eater. That said... I just love sweet potatoes...
What I like... um, it's not like I like it or hate it. Yes.
I've been eating a lot of Japanese food lately... maybe I like it more than I did before.
I eat Japanese food with him a lot these days. So I have come to like it.
There is a restaurant we've been frequenting lately, so I'm researching their menu.
There is a restaurant that he and I have been going to a lot lately, so I'm researching the menu there.
I'm really into Chinese food right now. Maybe it's because he eats a lot.
These days it's Chinese food. We often go out to eat together.
Hmm... when you have someone to cook for, you might naturally become that person's favorite... I'm kidding.
When I have someone to cook for, I can't help but like his taste... I wonder if I'm becoming more like him, I'm kidding.

I am 16 years old and a sophomore in high school.

I see... that's a bit surprising.

Oh, so you are just like him.

Okay, now me. What type am I？

Too bad, the correct answer was type A. Yes, I am like him. Maybe that's why we get along so well.

I see... I'd be a little happy if it was like that.
Really？ I think this may be the first time you've told me...

Do you think there is a blood type compatibility then？

Like, doing things at your pace, or something？
After all, the feeling of generosity？

Too bad... you're so kind to girls, I thought you had a little sister.
